Description['erl0001-exles2'] = "Advanced engineering unlocks T3 construction, more build power, resource, mobility & regen.   \n \n Build Power x9 from base value  \n Mass Production x5 from base value  \n Energy Production x25 from base value \n +14% Movement \n Regen +60% from base value "
